         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#CMR">
            <p>You who read this, pray for Michael, unworthy bishop of Antiocheia <supplied reason="subaudible">and</supplied> citizen. Unless you are reborn through water and the spirit, 
               you may not enter the kingdom of the heavens.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            
            <p>ἐὰν μὴ ἀναγεννηθῆτε δι’ ὕδατος καὶ πνεύματος, οὐ μὴ εἰσέλθητε εἰς τὴν βασιλείαν τῶν οὐρανῶν. Pseudo Clement 18.17</p>
         </div>
